###############
二、更新zookeeper
###############
------------- lzl oms 预售通知 -----------------------------
1、在zookeeper上增加节点：
	bg-oms-service > system.properties
	bg-oms-service > ice_config.xml
	
2、在system.properties中增加内容：
	oms.presale.notify.mobile=18377107705,13950309770,15018772548
  oms.presale.notify.email=jing.zhu@opi-corp.com,yan.xu1@opi-corp.com,yijun.liao@opi-corp.com,wenting.lei@opi-corp.com,juan.lai1@opi-corp.com,luying.lu@opi-corp.com 
  
3、在ice_config.xml中增加内容：
	<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
	<ice-config>
	    <springConfig>
	        <config>conf/spring/oms/bg-oms-config.xml</config> 
	    </springConfig>
	
	    <services>
	        <service identity="pmsService" 
	                         replicaGroup="pmsIceBoxReplicaGroup" 
	                         connectMode="prod"
	                         localPort="10012"/>
	        <service identity="omsService" 
	                         replicaGroup="omsIceBoxReplicaGroup" 
	                         connectMode="prod"
	                         localPort="10012"/>
	        <service identity="baseService" 
	                         replicaGroup="baseIceBoxReplicaGroup" 
	                         connectMode="prod"
	                         localPort="10008"/>
	    </services>
	</ice-config>
	
4、在task-web节点下的ice_config.xml增加
	<service identity="bg-omsService" 
                         replicaGroup="bg-omsIceBoxReplicaGroup" 
                         connectMode="dev"
                         localPort="10412"/>

-------------------- lsf base 短信 --------------------------
在/mlwconf/commons/messages.properties 文件中将message.guodo.url注释掉，并添加如下一行：
      message.guodo.url=http://221.179.180.158:9008/HttpQuickProcess/submitMessageAll



###############
三、编译发布程序代码
###############
--------------- 6.0.3 --------------------------------------
注：发布前需要增加bg-omsIceBox服务 并修改mq的发布脚本发布到对应的服务上 测试环境上已有

commons基础包：无

根据开发过程中涉及的模块发布：
	/data/compileAnddeploy/prod_release 下发布service
		 ./release.sh mlw-pms
		 ./release.sh mlw-oms
		 ./release.sh mlw-sp
		 ./release.sh mlw-base
		 ./release.sh mlw-cms2
		 ./release_mq.sh bg_oms  
		 


  /data/compileAnddeploy/prod_release 下发布web
  	 ./release_web.sh mlw-admin-web
  	 ./release_web.sh mlw-www-web
  	 ./release_web.sh mlw-passport-web
  	 ./release_web.sh mlw-cms2-web
  	 ./release_web.sh mlw-app-web
		 
  	
  /data/compileAnddeploy/prod_release 下发布静态资源
		 ./release_res.sh mlw-web-res


